Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.33,0:01:07.63,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}「人とは違う」で差をつけろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:13.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}コンビニの雑誌コーナー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}表紙にふとして書いてあった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:19.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.56,0:01:22.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}子供の頃は気にもせず
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}気に入らなければ怒って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.10,0:01:27.99,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}好きなものを好きだと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:31.16,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕らは変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.16,0:01:34.03,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}守りたいものが変わってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.03,0:01:36.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されない宝物から
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.85,0:01:39.52,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}理解されるための建前へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.52,0:01:45.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}大人になるほど　後悔する生き物になる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:47.67,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}でもね　それでもね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:52.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}見えるものがあるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.66,0:01:59.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}だから僕は僕らしく　そして君は君らしくって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:05.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}初めから　探すようなものではないんだと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:10.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}僕は君じゃないし　君も僕じゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.22,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}すれ違う　手をつなぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:17.83,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}そこには愛だって生まれる　そういうもんさ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:21.73,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}自分らしさってなんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.79,0:02:27.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変えられない　大切があるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:31.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(400,400)}変わりゆく生活が　正しい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You held out a small hand
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:33.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Smiling like to you it was so natural
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:38.63,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}It may have no meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:44.40,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it is something I cannot do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:50.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}You touched my hand without thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:54.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}but it was nice for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:21:02.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}All the time we believed
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:08.06,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}that the world was in our hands
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.25,0:21:10.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}We were wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:19.03,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}maybe it wasn't 'cause \Nyou're holding my hand now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:24.65,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}At every moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:30.19,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}Everywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:35.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}I can believe, I can believe
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:40.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}When I'm holding your warm hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:48.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(400,400)}your warm hand
